查佢既資料黎決定買唔買"},{"pid":"d3eaf123d9b321c031bbd15a7e38555cdc219023","tid":335152,"uid":37413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:57:23.000Z","msg":"教你老母， 根本香港人就識睇<br />\n唔買係你樣衰， 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"8f5a771616dfd7092f6e5f1f3ea6fb982b1e815d","tid":335152,"uid":35347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T13:58:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港係用繁體<br />\n你唔好話去美國賣唔到書 要叫美國人學中文?On lun79<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但美國人會咁做<br />\n美國文化唔受歡迎，就會抹黑人係恐怖國家，極權國家</blockquote><br />\n英文有乜問題<br />\n識唔識咩叫lingua franca?"},{"pid":"7b0fad724b699705843a229f9949121bc6ab0dc9","tid":335152,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:59:47.000Z","msg":"大陸版平唔平先，你平一半以上一定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}